{"tid":462086,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【屯門裘錦秋中學】47歲教師激戰18歲學生   雙雙被捕","createTime":"2017-11-08T08:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T04:48:35.000Z","uid":48093,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"2ce01dbe6bf0b1e92c1e8dd7d721d02e98d0feee","tid":462086,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:50:20.000Z","msg":"屯門楊青路28號一間中學，上午11時許，一名47歲姓錢教師與18歲姓黃男學生因教學問題爭執，其間學生揮拳襲擊老師，老師亦出拳還擊。警員接報到場，雙方均報稱受傷，一併送往屯門醫院治理。警方經初步調查，兩人均涉嫌傷人被拘捕。"},{"pid":"df32f2f2f0a57ac0bc7a696d6f18f988c7820c59","tid":462086,"uid":1082,"like":80,"dislike":1,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:51:57.000Z","msg":"47 歲真係人生既難關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e575468817a98a443e65ce03c400f7b4a1d12b5b","tid":462086,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:52:24.000Z","msg":"石丸vs青子"},{"pid":"7192b13b486c646584f315a0452a5bb64c955258","tid":462086,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:53:19.000Z","msg":"新武館？"},{"pid":"88ef2481abb752a13e0645d578c07df25519d9cb","tid":462086,"uid":108090,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:55:14.000Z","msg":"仲以為扑野<br />\n見到男同學 仲以為搞基"},{"pid":"e1d02f6f76d325cbf3f0b97082fc55dcfad571a6","tid":462086,"uid":48093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:55:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171108/large/1510130095_8d9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171108%2Flarge%2F1510130095_8d9b.jpg&h=40ca6969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姓錢教師(左)與學生(右)涉嫌在校園內打交，雙雙被拘捕"},{"pid":"03851e7a8cdacb29e3e735d2be82e0f6975d042f","tid":462086,"uid":26451,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:55:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b41e9075106e84f5a9fedcf71fb882e772045c1c","tid":462086,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:56:04.000Z","msg":"睇蘋果以為屌西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb7be6f6178f8f594aa77926a76ed8a3c603854","tid":462086,"uid":105067,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:56:45.000Z","msg":"47歲（入院）"},{"pid":"755575328a879204ac86521d9af011baf953c6fe","tid":462086,"uid":83623,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:57:14.000Z","msg":"連環拳打老師　中三生收監<br />\n教育界指政府愚蠢　助長校園暴力<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】裘錦秋中學一名16歲中三男生，疑不滿被老師罰企，竟出拳打傷老師眼部。涉案學生昨於荃灣裁判法院承認一項傷人罪，聲稱已有悔意，卻歸咎老師語氣重而肇禍，更指自己即將在其他學校開學，要求輕判。惟主任裁判官練錦鴻堅持將他還押監房至下月3日，待索閱感化官等報告始判。有教育界人士指事件反映校園暴力已亮起紅燈，元凶是政府政策「愚蠢」。<br />\n被告男生姓林，現年16歲，案發時就讀裘錦秋中學三年級。事緣今年4月22日，案中被襲的26歲男事主容樂其正在授課，惟被告男生與同學均無專心上課，半小時後，事主忍受不住，帶着有關的學生到另一課室，探討課室秩序問題。當時另一名中年男教師也在場。<br />\n<br />\n當年容總又係裘錦秋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c7c0a188a569f79e387d53e784e203e4f49b66","tid":462086,"uid":133223,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:57:27.000Z","msg":"47歲 (被捕)"},{"pid":"662ac6572d7bace10ecf1557b9c6d222c3d148ae","tid":462086,"uid":90766,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:57:34.000Z","msg":"屯門楊青路28號一間中學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同直接開名有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b87ebf69d26aab373d166288ad79a8ca99345ce","tid":462086,"uid":7700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:58:09.000Z","msg":"錢sir?"},{"pid":"51c22e8fda791bd1d6f436dafb4a5a9adabfa175","tid":462086,"uid":80294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"repl